{"tid":887633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寶可夢阿伯南下參戰！15支手機「扇形陣」抓稀有寶","createTime":"2018-11-03T05:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T12:43:56.000Z","uid":32511,"like":181,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"591a1dc27ee3717234a2b4ee50eaec6e6c5ae0c4","tid":887633,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"民眾瘋抓寶！《Pok幦on GO Safari Zone in Tainan》邁入第三天，也是周休首日，台南奇美博物館今（3）日上午就湧入大批玩家，知名的寶可夢阿伯今天也被捕獲，這次他架出15支手機，組成驚人「扇形陣」，準備大肆狩獵稀有寶！<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzQsHN4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzQsHN4.png&h=780ee4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本次在台南舉辦寶可夢活動，成功吸引全台各地玩家共襄盛舉，今天一早就有大批人潮進入奇美博物館，不分男女老少都蓄勢待發，要好好抓寶抓到爽，會場中也發現70歲的寶可夢阿伯，這次不僅「有備而來」還「更上層樓」，一次就架出15支手機，還熟練地撒櫻花、進行設定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rv4QFzX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRv4QFzX.png&h=2aa2c9ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eR76YmD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeR76YmD.png&h=ac1f860a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n寶可夢阿伯表示，這次自己從新北市土城開車南下，為了讓15支手機都能持續抓寶，包包內可是準備了大量的行動電源，「一顆大的就能撐20小時」，就等著與同好們前來會合，一起開心抓寶了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKBznOt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKBznOt.png&h=166bb7f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa7a6f0402711cc2d1cbbbc1f66caf3b6c1d06d1","tid":887633,"uid":52358,"like":425,"dislike":3,"score":422,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/mJxDUPi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmJxDUPi.jpg&h=89cd6258&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68133a821a127ee98d5adbcb1b31e471edd6b661","tid":887633,"uid":42374,"like":128,"dislike":8,"score":120,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37bb48f4209791257008