 />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3536/3536392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3536%2F3536392.jpg&h=d258e9f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亞瑟王墓地位於英國格拉斯頓伯里修道院（Glastonbury Abbey），寂寥的草皮底下就沉睡著傳說中的圓桌武士領袖，也是Fate系列女主角Saber的原型。但日本網友@hinata5dx遠渡重洋到來，竟然完整重現了Fate動畫的最後一幕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3536/3536388.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3536%2F3536388.jpg&h=54e3e17f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3536/3536389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3536%2F3536389.jpg&h=9849e1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朝聖之旅的重點果然還是手遊角色卡，日本網友隨即跪在亞瑟王的墓前，叨唸著「讓我抽中女主角的泳裝卡吧～～」但現實是殘酷的，當場花了日幣7萬元（約台幣2萬元）抽卡的結果還是槓龜。<br />\n<br />\n▼日本網友hinata5DX表示，在墓前跪著花7萬日幣，還是沒抽到泳裝亞瑟王角色卡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3536/3536391.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3536%2F3536391.jpg&h=5cd7ee17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消息回傳日本國內，立馬引起了FGO玩家間的佩服讚嘆與安慰，紛紛建議這位遠赴英國的重度玩家「沒抽到卡沒關係，放鬆心情去逛大英博物館吧」、「別難過，當作旅行的插曲吧」「亞瑟王如果知道自己被變性，還被套上泳裝，只會想出土爆揍你一頓」。<br />\n<br />\n能飛到歐洲求當歐洲人的玩家，肯定是不缺錢的，但面對現實，修道院裡的墓地只是紀念性質，並沒有埋藏屍骨，而且真實中的亞瑟王...是個男人啊。<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/38218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F38218&d=nfzWDI8azAY8tkzr8OBsXQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e2f7a42c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/38218</a>"},{"pid":"80b942bd678c695cf96d61366ad27b51be946a1a","tid":887633,"uid":13205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:55:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支那人根本就無得玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去過日本event，日本玩呢隻game咩年齡層都有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>pokemon go 一有社群日，好多時都係亞太區多人多到死server<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/36808/pokemon-go-beldum-community-day-broken-will-be-held-next-weekend\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F36808%2Fpokemon-go-beldum-community-day-broken-will-be-held-next-weekend&d=nfzWDI8azAY8tkzr8OBsXQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e05f33f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/36808/pokemon-go-beldum-community-day-broken-will-be-held-next-weekend</a></blockquote><br />\n死Server咪係因為個Server要load埋你呢啲仆街<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">外掛狗</span></span></strong>玩殘囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/aPyzOS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/aPyzOS</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/101024_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F101024_c28fde4b301245661917bae59eb18320.jpg&h=e0f1cbb3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}